      "text": "# 📖 Act 8: Ancient Rule\n**act** · swordsman · narrative · first_person\n\nTwo-of-Three Locks. Heavy Armor unlocks at fifteen attestations. Never hold all three locks in one agent."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "0afcd803d546d342",
      "text": "> *When one holds the sword, the vault, and the pen, corruption conceals itself—divide these across swordsman and mage, and betrayal becomes impossible to hide.*"
